<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Air Force may discharge an aviation cadet at any time.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idab6b1b68-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/545">70A Stat. 545</ref>, § 8817; renumbered § 9307, <ref href="/us/pl/115/232/dA/tVIII/s806/b/12">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VIII, § 806(b)(12)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1833">132 Stat. 1833</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
